org.jcvi.jillion.internal.trace.chromat.scf

Enum SCFCodecs

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<SCFCodecs>
      • org.jcvi.jillion.internal.trace.chromat.scf.SCFCodecs
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<SCFCodecs>, SCFCodec

    public enum SCFCodecs
extends Enum<SCFCodecs>
implements SCFCodec
    SCFCodecs contains singleton implementations of various SCFCodecs to parse each file format version of SCF encoded files.
    Author:
    dkatzel

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      VERSION_2
      Handles the legacy SCF 2.00 encoded SCF files.
      VERSION_3
      Handles SCF 3.00 (the current version) encoded SCF files.

      • encode

        protected final void encode(OutputStream out,
                            Chromatogram c,
                            int version)
                     throws IOException
        Encodes the given Chromatogram into SCF version specific format. If the chromatogram is not an instance of ScfChromatogram then those scf specific fields are left blank or empty.
        Parameters:
        out - the OutputStream to write the encoded Chromatogram.
        c - the Chromatogram to write.
        version - which SCF format version spec to encode.
        Throws:
        IOException - f there are any problems encoding the chromatogram or any problems writing to the OutputStream.
